  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Google just leaked something huge. A new Gemini video model called Omni was spotted inside the Create videos tab.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3b07c39b3408ff60cbc5b85b55218d3d846a16c8ed9ca6c64106a23260f68a24",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here is the exact text that leaked. Start with an idea or try a template.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0912b4a2afc1b14b00b4583d56ce96f137fbafd53e303fc3e420819b48b9ef0c",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Powered by Omni. That line appeared in Gemini's video creation UI.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8eeaaab17e9e4aac7c0b536be93c2a1f0b3566d07717471a83fa5d254284e4c0",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 34
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Spotted by Thomas on X. Verified by Testing Catalog.",
      "checksum": "sha256:757b61488ef76d339b0e3f3aedd9113e094fd4155eed58ebb4d32516b2ddbca5",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 45
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Today the same tab runs on a tool internally called Toucan.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38f3b4fe40ede4511e460db647aee8d7c9f0de410900e299ed2570ccdd6a196a",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 54
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And Toucan is powered by Veo 3.1. Google's current top video model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3cc7f9e1b14016ad105a7254fdf619fbc8c8188f9aa92b0de553d6402e27180c",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 65
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "So what does Omni actually mean? There are three honest possibilities.",
      "checksum": "sha256:18acd01f5f7f9a8bf59fd6c9dcf699100424ba538aed5569131b6de4ff2c3c72",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 77
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "None confirmed by Google. First. A simple rebrand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5ef1e653510decce519fb6c37a2e4529be0b04057a8107d4404b58aa1863fb01",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 88
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Same Veo tech, new product name. Second.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eb3dc37a0d8ebf438c9cae270ab9c134b2cce7e634f3f3597f6dfd0c4ffffe48",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 96
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "A brand new Gemini trained video model. Living alongside Veo for API users.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4f2cc62b6faf8cbdd63829f3e365dc7bcbdce204a4545326ef19d03d90b2406",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 103
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Third. The big one. A true unified omni model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e533f9d8fbe882a727cb1738ae4526bbdc66baeee4e4828ac6a62baec768e0d",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 116
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Generating image, video, and audio in one system.",
      "checksum": "sha256:426c72be1922236151bc2f1cfe47361fc7fe5ef08f3d7296184a6932dda8b1d0",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Testing Catalog called this highly speculative.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b98d2316a718146d9670b984252ca7b07e9263736d98622fe203b4aef701ad3",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Until Google confirms it, treat all three as guesses.",
      "checksum": "sha256:959e3ebeeae37773a545a6c72ab7db9bd39af38f356e6298c92407ac72722608",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 139
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Here is where it gets interesting. Google I/O 2026 lands on May 19 and 20.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c2ab1a90ebf353949fdb601edebb7782f7eb416224ee272a295f3aa38dfdccd3",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 148
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "That is just over two weeks away. The keynote drops May 19 at 10 AM Pacific.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de34f6232e9fb1ef59a80ebcf5f6727dfe8b00c851f9937e7217a4b40819b76a",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 163
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "We will cover every announcement on this channel.",
      "checksum": "sha256:77d57355e02514c7da2046829d0a85170503324274c09554247a1aba6dd47240",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 179
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "So tell me. Real omni model. Or just a clever Veo rebrand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dce9c18f0cc276f8f87e44524c9b4afb0a57707acc362d3084de757884d722a4",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 187
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Drop your guess in the comments. Hit subscribe.",
      "checksum": "sha256:18298b66b16eadd7b4919591e6cf6528a2f5141d59e01be55fa7fecd9b0d6629",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 199
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "We will know in 16 days.",
      "checksum": "sha256:019ecc03c7a8abdc6e5282c29af9226e7717867f781f5e4bae4d0cf9884ab617",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 1.6253968253968254,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 207
    }
  ]
